name: How many XTZ is your soul worth?
description:
/A hairy snake crushing your chest, the attack of a stinking goat, and bearing the stare of the evil eye of the Basilisco, these are the challenges you have to face if you want to survive the Salamanca.

Becoming the artist you want to be is not easy, even if you make a pact with the devil.

It is rumored that in the depths of Argentina there is a cave full of knowledge, where reaching the maximum potential depends only on you. You have to follow the music and let yourself be guided by a crow, once inside it will not be easy to get out, nor will it be easy to complete the stages, people without fear are the only ones capable of achieving it. 

Now there is something that I ask myself... How many XTZ is your soul worth?/

𝘛𝘰𝘳𝘯𝘢𝘥𝘰 𝘙𝘰𝘥𝘳𝘪𝘨𝘶𝘦𝘻 (@𝘵𝘰𝘳𝘯𝘢𝘥𝘰_𝘪𝘭𝘶𝘴) 𝘧𝘰𝘳 𝘵𝘩𝘦 '𝘖𝘶𝘳 𝘔𝘺𝘵𝘩𝘴' 𝘦𝘹𝘩𝘪𝘣𝘪𝘵𝘪𝘰𝘯 𝘩𝘦𝘭𝘥 𝘣𝘺 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘊𝘏𝘌𝘕 𝘢𝘳𝘵𝘪𝘴𝘵 𝘤𝘰𝘭𝘭𝘦𝘤𝘵𝘪𝘷𝘦
